oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Susan Porter on the Anderson farm washing clothes
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Susan Porter on the Anderson farm washing clothes. In the background there is a upturned iron wash kettle she had boiled her white clothes in to bleach them.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Laundry; Accessories (Clothing & dress)
